welcome to acosta  ramirez llc – juan acostareboyras welcome to acosta  ramirez llc we remain as a boutique law firm that provides the highest quality assistance in tax and corporate matters as such we are able to assist our clients in complex tax and corporate issues in a personal and efficient manner juan acostareboyrasprior to cofounding the firm mr acostareboyras was a partner and tax division director at two other prominent law firms in puerto rico and partner in charge of the san juan office tax division of a leading national accounting firm for approximately  years throughout his year career mr acostareboyras has dealt with a variety of tax compliance and planning issues while concentrating on taxrelated business affairs including corporate reorganizations mergers acquisitions and divestitures  he has also counseled clients on the organization and operation of corporations in puerto rico applications for grants of tax exemption and united states and puerto rico income tax matters dealing with outbound and inbound transfer of assets mr acostareboyras is a certified public accountant since  and licensed to practice law in the commonwealth of puerto rico and the united states court of appeals for the first circuit since   a former president of the puerto rico society of certified accountants he is an active  member of the puerto rico bar association the american bar association and the american institute of certified public accountants mr acostareboyras is a graduate of the university of puerto rico school of law and school of business  he has been chairman of the tax committee and a past member of the board of the puerto rico chamber of commerce mr acostareboyras is a frequent speaker on tax issues email jaracostaramirezcom rvnpolyontheme rvnpolyonthemetv rvnpolyonthemefwv fbp juan acostareboyras insider trades for first bancorp puerto rico bulletin investor alert tokyo markets open in us market snapshot currencies commodities expand keep open close expand keep